#

Mint Lemonade

10 min
$5
60 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

DrinkRefreshingSummer Drink

Description

A refreshing drink combining zesty lemon and cool mint, perfect for hydration!

Ingredients

  • fresh lemons: 2
  • fresh mint leaves: 1/4 cup
  • granulated sugar: 1/4 cup
  • cold water: 4 cups
  • ice cubes: as needed
